{
  "stem": "14724.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had to put up with my children crying because there was no way on anybody's Earth that I was allowed out again.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And life carried on like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had classes in the classrooms, in the orphanage, to continue our Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the boys-- mainly the boys-- were given classes in everything else, because we girls were too busy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had to run [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had to cook, and clean, and polish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Until one day, a photographer came to the orphanage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As I said, in those days, one didn't ask why.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And someone said, smile.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I have nothing to smile about, but you put a smile on your face.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I've still got the photograph.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I don't know how many photographs were taken.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I know mine was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we heard nothing for a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then I was called to the hall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then these orphanages are absolutely enormous places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And for a child-- I mean, in hindsight, they were big.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "For a child, they were unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I was called to the hall-- no telephone, you just send another child.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the superintendent sent for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I came down these massive steps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I could see somebody or something sitting in a chair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I got closer and closer-- I still didn't know who or what it was-- until I could completely [INAUDIBLE] next to him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[CRYING] I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was a big man with blond, curly hair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what I was looking at was a skeleton in clothes with no hair.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[CRYING] This was my father, [CRYING] the handsomest man I've ever known.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This skeleton was my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He'd been allowed out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sonny, could you get me a tissue, please?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I just don't seem to have any left.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
